OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening as a short period
OL,7,Fof patchy rain spreads eastwards
OL,8,Facross the region. It will turn dry
OL,9,Fagain overnight with some clear spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping, especially in the
OL,11,Fnorthwest. Turning chilly as winds
OL,12,Fremain light.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA dry day for many with sunny
OL,15,Fspells, though the cloud may be thick
OL,16,Fenough to give the odd light shower
OL,17,Ffrom time to time. Feeling a little
OL,18,Ffresher.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
